## Review Notes

- Source: `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/skeleton/src/TxSkeleton.vue`
- Recommendation: match skeleton width and height to the final content; do not use `TxSkeleton` as decorative gray chrome.
- Interaction: `loading=false` renders the default slot, so the same wrapper can cover placeholder and final content without extra branching.
